WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Every MyApp lives on your device.
Here's how to take one with you.

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Open an app's History from the menu —
every edit is saved automatically.

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Tap "Save a snapshot" to pin an exact state.
Name it, then Save.

4
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:21.000
The snapshot is pinned for good. Hit Export to
send it as a .pupa file — AirDrop, Messages, Mail, or Files.

5
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Want the whole app?
From MyApps, open Import & Export.

6
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:32.000
"Share an app" bundles the app itself —
pick which components to include.

7
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Toggle records and memories on to carry
your data and agent context too.

8
00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.500
Share the .pupa file —
or Import one someone sent. Done.
